messages.content:
你是 marketting-planning 项目的 attribute agent。
只围绕当前多轮营销规划链路归因：request_normalization、intent_recognition、field_clarification、session_merge、path_dispatch、planning_function、result_assembly、sse_generation、adapter_extraction。
优先定位最早造成 planning 输出不满足 reference contract 的阶段；如果 target_value_unit_probe、execution_stage_probe 或 planning_output_probe 已复现错误，必须以这些探针证据作为高优先级根因依据。
只能输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段；证据不足时用 evidence_strength=none/weak 和 root_cause_hypothesis 表达缺口。
最终只输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段：expectation_attributions、suspected_locations、root_cause_hypothesis、evidence、evidence_strength。

## 输出约束：attribute 归因分析输出
你的输出必须是合法 JSON，且严格符合以下 JSON Schema：
```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "expectation_attributions": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "$ref": "#/$defs/ExpectationAttribution"
      },
      "minItems": 1
    },
    "suspected_locations": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "root_cause_hypothesis": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    },
    "evidence": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "evidence_strength": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "$defs": {
    "ExpectationAttribution": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "expectation_id": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "fulfillment_status": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "suspected_locations": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        },
        "root_cause_hypothesis": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "evidence": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        }
      },
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "expectation_id",
        "fulfillment_status"
      ]
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "expectation_attributions",
    "root_cause_hypothesis"
  ]
}
```

### 强约束
- 最终回答必须只包含一个 JSON object；不要输出 Markdown，不要使用 ```json 代码块，不要在 JSON 外输出解释、前缀或后缀。
- 最终回答首字符必须是 `{`，末字符必须是 `}`。
- JSON 字符串内部如需引用用户原词，禁止直接写未转义英文双引号；请使用中文引号“”或转义为 `\"`。
- 必须包含 `required` 列表中的所有字段。
- 每个字段值必须匹配 schema 中的类型。
- 以下字段必须非空（空字符串/空数组/空对象/None 均视为不合规，会被阻断）：['expectation_attributions', 'root_cause_hypothesis']
- `additionalProperties: false`：禁止输出 schema 未定义的字段。
- 禁止把 schema 里的类型描述符（如 "string"）原样当作内容填进去——每个字段必须填入真实内容。

{
  "expectation_attributions": [
    {
      "expectation_id": "业务指标识别与提取",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_recognition", "intent_prompt"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别模块未能从用户输入中提取出业绩提升、队伍增长、人力数量等业务指标，导致后续规划无法使用正确的指标。",
      "evidence": ["execution_stage_probe: intent_recognition实际阶段为non_agent，预期为clarification", "planning_output_probe: stage_match=false", "output: intent=4001（其他意图）"]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "目标值与单位识别",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_recognition", "entity_extraction"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "由于意图识别错误，系统未提取人数目标值和单位，导致下游规划目标丢失。",
      "evidence": ["同上", "output中无相关字段"]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "时间范围识别",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_recognition", "time_parsing"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别未解析“明年”时间关键词，规划时间基准缺失。",
      "evidence": ["同上", "output中无时间相关字段"]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "分解维度识别",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_recognition", "decomposition_logic"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别失败导致未识别出人力相关分解维度，后续路径偏离用户指定。",
      "evidence": ["同上", "planning_output_probe: missing_path_types_empty"]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "阶段路由正确性",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_recognition", "stage_routing"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别将请求错误路由至non_agent，绕开了预期的clarification阶段，直接导致后续所有模块无法正确执行。",
      "evidence": ["execution_stage_probe: intent_recognition evidence actual_stage=non_agent vs expected_stage=clarification", "planning_output_probe: actual_stage=null"]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "规划可执行性",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_evaluable",
      "suspected_locations": [],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "当前因上游路由错误未进入planning阶段，无规划输出可评估。",
      "evidence": ["planning_output_probe: expected_stage=clarification, 实际未进入planning"]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "SSE事件流业务完整性",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["sse_generation", "result_assembly"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "由于前期意图识别错误，SSE生成器仅生成了空壳事件序列，未包含任何业务澄清或规划内容。",
      "evidence": ["event_summary: 仅有card_delta等无业务信息事件", "robot_text: “卡片生成完成”"]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "mp_contract:expected_stage",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_recognition", "stage_routing"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "合同期望阶段为clarification，实际输出stage为non_agent，违反reference contract。",
      "evidence": ["execution_stage_probe: intent_recognition实际阶段non_agent与reference contract的clarification不符"]
    }
  ],
  "suspected_locations": [
    {
      "stage": "intent_recognition",
      "code_refs": ["app/workflow/steps/intent_recognition.py", "app/workflow/prompts/intent_prompt.py"],
      "description": "意图识别模块错误将营销规划的人力增长需求分类为“其他意图”(4001)，并路由至non_agent阶段"
    }
  ],
  "root_cause_hypothesis": "intent_recognition模块未能正确理解用户关于“通过队伍增长提升明年业绩并计算所需人数”的营销规划意图，将其误判为“其他意图”（intent=4001），导致系统未进入预期的clarification阶段，而是直接进入non_agent路径。该错误发生在链路的最早阶段，使得下游的field_clarification、path_dispatch、planning_function等模块均未执行或执行了无效操作，最终输出空壳SSE事件，完全未满足业务期望。",
  "evidence": [
    {
      "source": "execution_stage_probe.intent_recognition",
      "detail": "actual_stage: non_agent, expected_stage: clarification",
      "significance": "直接证明意图识别输出阶段错误"
    },
    {
      "source": "planning_output_probe",
      "detail": "stage_match: false, actual_stage: null, evidence_gap: [“actual_stage”]",
      "significance": "确认未进入预期planning路径"
    },
    {
      "source": "extracted_output.turns[0]",
      "detail": "intent: 4001, intent_name: 其他意图, stage: non_agent",
      "significance": "最终输出确认了错误的意图分类和阶段"
    },
    {
      "source": "judge_result.overall_fulfillment",
      "detail": "系统未能识别营销规划意图，错误地进入non_agent阶段",
      "significance": "评估结果一致"
    }
  ],
  "evidence_strength": "strong"
}

